conversations.content: I have many items in my cart and want to clear out everything except for the electric toothbrush. Please remove the other items and place the order.

<|Function_Thought|>
The cart contains three items, with product IDs: P001 for TechBrand Wireless Mouse, P017 for Backpack, and P011 for Electric Toothbrush. I need to remove the items with product IDs P001 and P017, and then proceed to checkout with the electric toothbrush (product ID P011).
<|/Function_Thought|>

<|Final_Answer|><|/Final_Answer|>

<|Function_Call|>[cart_remove_product(product_id="P001")]<|/Function_Call|>
Product ID P001 removed from cart.

<|Function_Thought|>
The TechBrand Wireless Mouse (Product ID: P001) has been successfully removed from the cart. Now, I need to remove the Backpack (Product ID: P017) before proceeding to checkout the Electric Toothbrush.
<|/Function_Thought|>

<|Final_Answer|><|/Final_Answer|>

<|Function_Call|>[cart_remove_product(product_id="P017")]<|/Function_Call|>
Product ID P017 removed from cart.

<|Function_Thought|>
Both the TechBrand Wireless Mouse and the Backpack have been successfully removed from the cart. I will now proceed to checkout the remaining item, the Electric Toothbrush.
<|/Function_Thought|>

<|Final_Answer|><|/Final_Answer|>

<|Function_Call|>[checkout_selected_cart(product_ids=["P011"], discount_code=null)]<|/Function_Call|>
